# `manifest.json` Schema

The `manifest.json` file is used for the Progressive Web App (PWA) configuration.

Refer to the existing [manifest.json](mdc:manifest.json) as a template.

## Required Properties

-   **`name`**: The full name of the application.
-   **`short_name`**: A shorter name for the application.
-   **`description`**: A short description of the application.
-   **`start_url`**: The entry point for the application.
-   **`display`**: The display mode (e.g., `fullscreen`, `standalone`).
-   **`theme_color`**: The primary theme color for the UI.
-   **`background_color`**: The background color of the splash screen.
-   **`icons`**: An array of icon objects for different resolutions.

## Icon Object Properties

-   **`src`**: The path to the icon image.
-   **`sizes`**: The dimensions of the icon (e.g., `192x192`).
-   **`type`**: The MIME type of the icon (e.g., `image/png`).
